full_text:
Rebecca Ryan  is an English actress. She attended St Monica's High School in Manchester. Ryan is best known for playing the role of Debbie Gallagher in the Channel 4 drama series Shameless  from 2004 to 2009, Carly Hope in the ITV soap opera Emmerdale in 2006, and as Vicki MacDonald in the BBC school drama Waterloo Road  from 2009 to 2011.
